README

PREREQUISITES:
- Ubuntu 22.04.X LTS
- ROS Humble
    > https
- GADEN2 (commit aa80f85, included)
    > https
- Crazyswarm2 (dev-sim-ros branch, commit 074ecd3, included)
    > https

COMPONENTS:
- launch files 
    > ros_ws/src/crazyswarm/launch
- scripts 
    > ros_ws/src/crazyswarm/scripts
- GADEN files, sim only (room setup, wind sim.)
    > ros_ws/src/gaden/test_env/10x6_empty_room

USAGE:
start a terminal(ctrl + alt + t) in the launch folder
Simulation example: roslaunch APF_1_1.launch sim:=1
Real-world example: roslaunch field_APF_1.launch

TROUBLESHOOTING:
- make sure the entries in the crazyflies.yaml and launch file match
- make sure the radio channel (crazyflies.yaml) and url (script) match the url of the real drones
- ...

